ices management inc hsm a healthcare information technology consultant whose clients include allscripts athenahealth cerner and epic systems adi strategies on may   huron acquired adi strategies inc an enterprise performance management and business intelligence firm that has been recognized as an oracle platinum partner myroundingedit on february   huron acquired myrounding a firm specializing in digital health solutions to improve patient care cloudedit on october   huron acquired cloud a firm specializing in complex salesforcecom implementations and related cloudbased applications rittman mead indiaedit on july   huron acquired the india affiliate of rittman mead consulting ltd rittman mead india a data and analytics consulting firm that specializes in the implementation of enterprise performance management and analytics systems studer groupedit on feb   huron acquired studer group a professional services firm that consults with healthcare providers on clinical outcomes and financial results sky analyticsedit on jan   huron acquired sky analytics a massachusettsbased provider of legal software for corporate law departments threshold consulting incedit on oct   huron acquired threshold consulting inc a consulting firm that provides customer relationship management consulting cloudbased software as a service applications business intelligence solutions and data warehousing vonlay llcedit on may   huron acquired vonlay llc a healthcare technology consulting firm specializing in clinical administrative and financial system implementation and optimization frankel groupedit on january   huron acquired the frankel group associates llc a life sciences consulting firm  blue stone internationaledit on september   huron acquired blue stone international llc a provider of oracle corporation professional services supporting enterprise performance management information management and business intelligence solutions under the terms of the agreement huron will acquire the assets