 with strategic operational management and financial challenges and develops and implements moneysaving procurement plans huron serves customers in the education professionalservices transportation healthcare telecom financial services electronics consumer products energy and utilities industrial manufacturing and food and beverage industries the company was founded in  and is headquartered in chicago detailed description  west van buren streetchicago il united statesfounded in  employees phone  fax  wwwhuronconsultinggroupcom key executives for huron consulting group inc mr james h roth cofounder ceo president  director age  total annual compensation k mr c mark hussey chief operating officer and executive vice president age  total annual compensation k ms diane e ratekin executive vice president general counsel and corporate secretary age  total annual compensation k compensation as of fiscal year  huron consulting group inc key developments huron appoints john westwood as managing director and global head of huron’s life sciences practice jun   huron announced that life sciences and strategy thought leader john westwood has joined the company as managing director and global head of huron’s life sciences practice he will lead the team that partners with pharmaceutical biotech and medical device organizations to develop strategies for innovating and delivering better medicines and outcomes for patients and healthcare providers and payers westwood will provide leadership to huron’s global life sciences experts as they guide clients through complex strategic payer and regulatory challenges that cross the healthcare sector he will focus on accelerating huron’s growth in the pharmaceutical biotech and medical device industries and continuing to expand its global business this includes enhancing huron’s support of life sciences organizations in the areas of strategy pricing reimbursement and transactions while drawing on huron’s expertise and presence in the healthcare and education sectors westwood has more than  years of experience working with life sciences companies worldwide he has advised more than  organizations on issues such as corporate and business unit strategy commercialization strategies portfolio design and transactions westwood most recently served as senior partner and managing director at lek consulting where he cofounded the firm’s life sciences practice and was responsible for its vision strategy and operations huron consulting group inc presents at the william blair  growth stock conference jun  am jun   huron consulting group inc presents at the william blair  growth stock conference jun  am venue the four seasons hotel  east delaware place chicago il  united states speakers james h roth cofounder chief executive officer president and director john d kelly chief financial officer executive vice president and treasurer huron consulting group inc presents at benchmark company llc oneonone investor conference jun may   huron consulting group inc presents at benchmark company llc oneonone investor conference jun  venue palmer house hilton  e monroe street chicago illinois united states similar private companies by industry company name region  payroll  hr services inc united states  water audit llc united states collegecom inc united states d research llc united states  partners llc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target mergeracquisition april   adi strategies inc mergeracquisition february   innosight llc mergeracquisition january   pope woodhead  associates ltd request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup most searched private companies company name geographic region la