 before using the material as you intend more info home  huron lets get to work at huron we believe this is a better way to achieve the type of change that delivers longterm success for our clients it takes genuine collaboration deep expertise and steady focus it takes true partnership from day one  sustainable enduring change doesn’t just happen it requires a dedicated partner to produce measurable longlasting results – results that improve performance today help chart the course for tomorrow and prepare our clients for the challenges of the future it’s this passionate commitment to our clients’ success that drives us we are huron let’s get to work choose your industry aerospace automotive consumer products energy and utilities engineering and construction financial services healthcare higher education hospitality and gaming life sciences logistics manufacturing metals and mining retail technology media and telecommunications choose your interest capabilities education experience experts insights start subscribe to huron insights sign up to get all of the great huron insights newsletter subscriptions growth challenge acceptedhuron and innosight are collaborating with clients to create tomorrows growth engines read more  ceo forum reportlearn strategies to transform your organization download report revolutionizing healthcare with disruptive innovationstrategies for building a future of better health and lower costs read more healthcare strategy clinical finance operations technology  coaching higher education strategy operations technology  research life sciences strategy compliance  operations business advisory advisory operations turnaround  valuation enterprise solutions  analytics erp epm crm  business analytics technology software partner  proprietary tools culture and community by recruiting retaining and developing a diverse workforce we are better able to meet the needs of our clients and create opportunities for all our ability to attract and retain exceptional professionals with diverse backgrounds and life experiences helps us bring more innovative creative and unique ideas and approaches to how we deliver excellent service and solutions to clients read more careers imagine looking back on your career  or  years from now how will it feel to know that you helped organizations that better our communities achieve meaningful change this legacy begins when you ignite your passion to make a difference you know that the mark you leave on the world matters read more investor relations huron consulting group inc is a public company traded on the nasdaq global select market under the symbol “hurn” huron consulting group is committed to its clients its people and its stockholders read more news  huron announces second quarter  earnings release and webcast  life sciences industry veteran joins huron to expand global business see all news huron consulting group  wikipedia huron consulting group from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search huron consulting group inc type public traded as nasdaq hurn industry management consulting business advisory business performance management education finance life sciences healthcare founded  headquarters chicago illinois area served worldwide key people james h roth ceo  president c mark hussey coo  cfo  treasurer revenue  million  operating income  million  net income  million  total assets  billion  total equity  million  number of employees   website wwwhuronconsultinggroupcom founded in  the huron consulting group commonly known as simply huron is a global management consulting company offering services to the healthcare higher education life sciences and commercial industries in fiscal year ending december   huron generated  million in annual revenue contents  history  recent acquisitions  myrounding  cloud  rittman mead india  studer group  sky analytics  threshold consulting inc  vonlay llc  frankel group  blue stone international  click commerce  revenue  financial restatement  recognition  references  external links historyedit huron was founded in may  in chicago illinois the company’s initial employees included former consultants from arthur andersen including  partners and  other professionals as of  huron had more than  employees in may  huron filed a registration statement with the securities and exchange commission sec relating to the initial public offering of its common stock huron consulting group inc the holding company became a public company trading common stock on the nasdaq global select market exchange under the ticker “hurn” in october  recent acquisitionsedit hsm on july   huron acquired healthcare services management inc hsm a healthcare information technology consultant whose clients include allscripts athenahealth cerner and epic systems adi strategies on may   huron acquired adi strategies inc an enterprise performance management and business intelligence firm that has been recognized as an oracle platinum partner myroundingedit on february   huron acquired myrounding a firm specializing in digital health solutions to improve patient care cloudedit on october   huron acquired cloud a firm specializing in complex salesforcecom implementations and related cloudbased applications rittman mead indiaedit on july   huron acquired the india affiliate of rittman mead consulting ltd rittman mead india a data and analytics consulting firm that specializes in the implementation of enterprise performance management and analytics systems studer groupedit on feb   huron acquired studer group a professional services firm that consults with healthcare providers on clinical outcomes and financial results sky analyticsedit on jan   huron acquired sky analytics a massachusettsbased provider of legal software for corporate law departments threshold consulting incedit on oct   huron acquired threshold consulting inc a consulting firm that provides customer relationship management consulting cloudbased software as a service applications business intelligence solutions and data warehousing vonlay llcedit on may   huron acquired vonlay llc a healthcare technology consulting firm specializing in clinical administrative and financial system implementation and optimization frankel groupedit on january   huron acquired the frankel group associates llc a life sciences consulting firm  blue stone internationaledit on september   huron acquired blue stone international llc a provider of oracle corporation professional services supporting enterprise performance management information management and business intelligence solutions under the terms of the agreement huron will acquire the assets of blue stone for  million in cash  click commerceedit huron acquired click commerce a supplier of softwarebased solutions and professional services to academic medical centers and research institutions terms of the acquisition were not disclosed revenueedit                       financial restatementedit on july   huron announced that the company would restate its financial statements for    and first quarter  that same day huron announced the resignation of its chairman of the board and ceo gary holdren cfo gary burge and that chief accounting officer wayne lipski would soon be departing the company also announced that james h roth a founder of the company would be hurons new ceo the following business day  august    huron’s shares dropped  percent to  the company had reported that shareholders of four huron business acquisitions acquired between  and  conditionally redistributed portions of their initial and future acquisitionrelated payments among themselves and to certain huron employees without hurons knowledge or permission the issue was initially identified by the chief accounting officercontroller wayne lipski on july   huron announced it has reached a final settlement with the us securities and exchange commission sec resolving the previously disclosed sec investigation into the company’s august  restatement of its financial statements for the years ended   and  and the first quarter of  the company agreed to the settlement without admitting or denying the sec’s findings recognitionedit huron was named one of forbes america’s best employers for  and  huron was named one of consulting magazine’s best firms to work for in      and  huron received consulting magazine’s excellence in social  community investment award in   and  consulting magazine named gordon mountford executive vice president huron healthcare as one of the top  most influential consultants in  consulting magazine named laura yaeger founding member and leader of huron consulting groups education and life sciences practice as one of the top  consultants in  consulting magazine named dr andrew ziskind managing director and clinical solutions leader huron healthcare as one of the top  most influential consultants in  consulting magazine named james h roth ceo and president as one of the top  most influential consultants in  and  the turnaround management association tma recognized huron as one of the winners of the  tma turnaround and transaction of the year awards huron financial was honored for its turnaround of bancroft bag inc huron healthcare was ranked in the top five of modern healthcare’s largest healthcare management consulting firms for the past  years huron was named a  and  top workplace by the oregonian huron was named a  and  top workplace by the chicago tribune hurons ecrt click and efacs were selected as readers choice top products by university business in   and  respectively huron received a perfect score on the human rights foundation’s corporate equality index in    and  referencesedit  a b c d e f g h i j k l m n huron consulting group inc k sec  retrieved     andersen employees resign to create own firm chicago tribune retrieved    huron consulting files for m ipo boston business journal retrieved    huron consulting ipo takes flight marketwatch retrieved    huron still buying 